# CI/CD Pipeline Guide

## Purpose
- Automate testing
- Build containers
- Deploy to environments
- Run security scans
- Manage releases
- Notify on events (Email)

## Implementation
- GitHub Actions or GitLab CI
- Multi-environment deployment
- Automated testing
- Security scanning
- Semantic versioning
- Email notifications

## Environment Variables
- GITHUB_TOKEN
- EMAIL_USER
- EMAIL_PASSWORD
